Package: CCR
Title: Contextual Concept Representation (CCR)
Version: 1.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Tom", "Zhang", email = "zhangsiyuan777@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Mohammad", "Atari", email = "m.atari.psy@gmail.com", role = "ctb")
    )
Description: Conduct theory-driven psychological text analysis by mutating a set of text and a psychometric scale into word embeddings using pre-trained transformers; where cosine similarities are then calculated to compare the text of interest with the psychometric scale items.
URL: https://github.com/tomzhang255/CCR
